Q8.1: Hereditary ataxia multigene panel (e.g., CPT 81443, 81479, 0216U, or 0217U)
Q17: To submit a claim, ensure the test requested is a hereditary ataxia multigene panel using an appropriate single panel CPT code (e.g., 81443, 81479, 0216U, or 0217U), provide documentation of pre- and post-test genetic counseling, confirm no prior testing of the requested genes, include documentation from the ordering provider on how results will impact medical care, and ensure all required information (ICD code, place of service, etc.) is included for automated processing. Claims for WGS are not covered under this policy.
